prompts.value: Could you please help me with the type of the masters you are interested in?

messages.speech: The minimum qualification to apply for graduate program is to have an undergraduate degree (BASc / B.Sc. in Engineering / B.Eng. degree or equivalent*) with at least 73% average over the last two years. International applicants are advised to refer to the specified minimum admission requirements, listed by country, at the Faculty of Engineeringâ€™s Professional and Graduate Studies (FEPGS) website and the Faculty of Graduate Studies website. Also have minimum score in any one of them IELTS (6.5)/GRE/TOEFL (IBT-92)/Pearson (65).
